init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They go from 1 down to 4 in order of their actual current ranking.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man who said he was ranked 1 is now 2 and his kid says "You're number 2?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So when you have the top 4 in the world at number 1, thats quite a bragging rights.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So there again we have a case of daddy being proud to have a "#1 DAD" mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So what happens when someone gets that number 1 ranking ?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They get to be the number 1 dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think my dad is the best dad in the world and he could get that number 1, best in the world title.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I just don't think dads want to be that number 2 dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: That's the one that makes your kid go to you mom and say "Hey look dad, you're number 2?" or worse yet #4 Dad

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So what happens when someone is ranked number 1 ?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They get a nice mug and they get to call themselves the number 1 dad in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Its a funny thing to do but we have all seen that life is about bragging rights.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So whats that #1 Dad mug doing for the company ?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: For one, they have a #1 Dad mug out there which is good for sales.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The company must be selling a lot of those mugs because they have to come up with more and more of them as the Dads out there buy

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the mugs so they can call themselves the "#1 Dad".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I don't think it sells as much as the "World's Greatest Dad" mug, but i'm sure it sells well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But hey we will just call you the best dad in the world because of a mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So if you are the best Dad out there, make sure you show off that #1 dad mug this fathers day.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know my dad would be proud to have a number 1 dad mug, so will you. :-)

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is a symbol of pride for dads out there to have the #1 Dad mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is a perfect example of marketing at it's finest.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So many people ask me if I have a #1 Dad mug and i say yes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I get a lot of compliments when I have it on display.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I always tell them that I'm number 1 Dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are like"Are you sure that isn't your mom's mug?"
